The paper deals with autonomous service robots and their ability to perform cleaning tasks using learning from demonstration paradigm. This involves the use of convolutional neural networks to generalize demonstrations to different dirt or stain patterns on the same table using only visual feedback. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
